                        <interp inst="t18560204-name-451" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS OAKLEY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, V</hi> 190). I produce a certificate—(<hi rend="italic">Read: Surrey Sessions—John Attwood, convicted March</hi>, 1855, <hi rend="italic">and confined three months</hi>)—I was present—the prisoner is the person.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
GUILTY</hi>.** Aged 19.—<hi rend="italic">
